# Vercel CLI deploys from the local filesystem, not git — .gitignore alone isn't enough to keep
# a local .env out of the uploaded bundle (see the incident this file fixes: a stray local .env
# shipped in a deploy and short-circuited the /tmp SQLite fallback in src/lib/db.ts with a
# read-only-filesystem error). Never remove this without understanding why it's here.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

test-results/
playwright-report/
tests-e2e/
